Name: SimonElf
  Simon's clone in ruby and lua under blendelf

License:
  Same as blendelf

Version:
  0.2

Copyright:
  Copyright (c) 2010 [Carlos Bola√±os](http://urbin.es).

Dependencies:
  - Blendelf ruby ext (http://github.com/cartuchogl/blendelf) for ruby version
  - bullet, sdl, ...
  
Usage:
  For ruby version "ruby simon.rb"
  For lua version "./blendelf simon.lua"

Notes:
  - If you are not using my fork of blendelf rename simon.lua to init.lua
  - Ruby version only tested on snow leopard but not stable.
  - sounds from http://simplythebest.net/sounds/WAV/events_WAV/alarm_wavs.html
